{"tid":518849,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[中伏?]agxda訂酒店揀延後付款竟然偷偷地收多錢","createTime":"2018-01-03T18:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T18:53:55.000Z","uid":82344,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e86f2fa5ebb13adf330b5ba6d3691e06db2307d6","tid":518849,"uid":82344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T18:02:38.000Z","msg":"預訂可揀即時比錢或者遲幾日比，講明遲比唔會收多，行程未firm嘅會揀<br />\n匯率就按付款日計<br />\n即係可以搏匯率會跌比少啲<br />\n當然升就比多啲<br />\n但係我一睇，發現明明匯率無點變<br />\n佢都可以收多左總數5%<br />\n雖然個數唔係多，但係無啦啦收多左條氣好唔順囉<br />\n如果個價唔係寫明呢個我都唔會用佢book啦<br />\n上網睇到好多人都係揀左延後付款之後收多左錢<br />\n<br />\n港女<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1575693/Agoda%E8%A8%82%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%80%E8%82%9A%E6%B0%A3%E3%80%80%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%936.6%E7%AB%9F%E4%BB%A57.9%E7%AE%97%EF%BC%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1575693%2FAgoda%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2582%259A%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%259C%25936.6%25E7%25AB%259F%25E4%25BB%25A57.9%25E7%25AE%2597%25EF%25BC%2581&d=pLCesClYAPxr%2FfDWnLqOdNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=03f42bce\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1575693/Agoda%E8%A8%82%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%80%E8%82%9A%E6%B0%A3%E3%80%80%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%936.6%E7%AB%9F%E4%BB%A57.9%E7%AE%97%EF%BC%81</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/showthread.php?t=1870561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.backpackers.com.tw%2Fforum%2Fshowthread.php%3Ft%3D1870561&d=pLCesClYAPxr%2FfDWnLqOdNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=91f55ed6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/showthread.php?t=1870561</a><br />\n<br />\n如果同佢地反映好似有得賠返現金，有台仔打埋教學...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://travelerliv.com/blog/post/222723240-%5B%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%5D-2017%E5%B9%B4agoda%E8%A8%82%E6%88%BF%E5%88%B7%E5%8D%A1%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%89%8B%E7%BA%8C%E8%B2%BB%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E9%80%80%E6%AC%BE\" data-sr-ur